# Regenerable caches. These rebuild deterministically from the logged seeds
# (see the reproducibility statement), so they are kept out of the repo.
data/truth_cache.pkl            # C2-C4 ground-truth bifurcation + VGTT cache
data/ground_truth_*.pkl         # C1 ground-truth bifurcation cache
data/segcache/                  # per-config training segments (md5-seeded)
data/*.log

# Deliberately NOT ignored (shipped so figures reproduce from cache):
